		Ok first of all, i found TauRuS releases from dupecheck.
		Although they said following in their nfo:

		&quot;This is for all our Swedish Asterix-fans out there 
		Skipped other audio and the Norwegian speaked version
		Every movie is done different, we concentrated only to
		keep swedish-audio, but some subs and other audios can
		still be left on some of the movies.&quot;

		So after investigating I still got no idea which audios you
		removed. But with same words this release pack would go like:

		&quot;This is for all our FiNNiSH Asterix-fans out there! 
		Although 4 of 6 movies have everything untouched,
		those two which had to be ripped&amp;encoded are:

		Asterix.Le.Gaulois.1967.PAL.DVDR-iSOF
		Asterix.Et.Cleopatra.1968.PAL.DVDR-iSOF

		And with these I ripped off all other audios than
		english and finnish (subs r there tho).

		Every movie is done with love, I concentrated only to
		keep finnish-audio, but every subs and other audios are
		left on 4 of these sweet movies.&quot;

		And for advice to TauRuS, when you do something,
		please specify which is left and which is not,
		it's not a big thing in big releases like these and
		it saves time from many. Thank you.
